{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"cdc37583-3e6a-461a-aa8c-85089939c23a","content":"Good news — in .NET 10, `dotnet test` natively uses Microsoft.Testing.Platform, so **`TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` is no longer needed**. That property was a bridge for .NET 9 and earlier SDKs. You can safely remove it.\n\nYou **do** still need `EnableMSTestRunner` — that's what builds your test project as an MTP executable.\n\nHere's the cleanup:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01A9FE7HwcsoVU867MrJJaq5","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Removing obsolete MTP property"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_0136YD8zTT39tjdisiYPbAhy","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-2cdd47bd8e444d6e9301d05b450c5440/TestProject.csproj","old_str":"    <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>\n","new_str":""},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-2cdd47bd8e444d6e9301d05b450c5440/TestProject.csproj."}],"interactionId":"5bbc7581-99f3-4036-8d97-0411c73fa399","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is on .NET 10 SDK (10.0.100) and wants to know about Microsoft.Testing.Platform (MTP) support in `dotnet test`.\n\nIn .NET 10, `dotnet test` has native MTP support built-in. The `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` property is no longer needed because .NET 10's `dotnet test` natively speaks the MTP protocol.\n\nHowever, they still need `EnableMSTestRunner` to build the test project as an executable that uses Microsoft.Testing.Platform.\n\nLet me verify my knowledge: In .NET 10, `dotnet test` was rewritten to use Microsoft.Testing.Platform natively. The old VSTest-based `dotnet test` is gone (or deprecated). The `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` property was a bridge for .NET 9 and earlier SDKs to make `dotnet test` work with MTP-based test projects. In .NET 10, this is the default behavior, so the property is unnecessary.\n\n\nNow I'll provide the guidance on how to set this up correctly.","outputTokens":549,"requestId":"1BC0:349D35:209173B:23FE068:6A03CF6C"},"id":"ad3d347b-fea7-4da5-ad69-fd6aaf893e90","timestamp":"2026-05-13T01:10:14.353Z","parentId":"f93018e6-185e-47bf-ba47-8314e091a30f"}
